&lt;p&gt;KKR’s Human Capital Benefits &amp;amp; Wellness team is responsible for implementing and enhancing the benefits programs and healthcare services for all KKR employees. The team analyzes workflows and technology solutions to align with the firm’s culture and value while providing optimal experiences. The team is also involved in every employees’ journey at KKR, from onboarding to off-boarding, travel and transfers, and even personal and professional milestones including work anniversaries..&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;POSITION SUMMARY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
