&lt;p&gt;KKR is seeking a collaborative, strategic, and detail-oriented professional to help evolve KKR’s Global Travel program.&amp;nbsp; This role will provide support to the Global Head of Travel to ensure service excellence and drive ongoing efficiencies and savings across KKR’s travel partners including designated travel company, corporate card, lodging, aviation and ground transportation providers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an outstanding opportunity for someone who thrives in a&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;high-touch, high-accountability environment&lt;/strong&gt; and wants to contribute meaningfully to a mission-critical corporate function.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RESPONSIBILITIES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
