&lt;p&gt;The Associate will play a key role in evaluating and executing M&amp;amp;A and strategic initiatives, including acquisitions that enhance the insurance business of KKR, reinsurance transactions, and internal strategic projects. This is a highly dynamic role suited for candidates interested in shaping the growth trajectory of a scaled insurance business.&lt;/p&gt;
