&lt;h2 data-start=&quot;233&quot; data-end=&quot;246&quot;&gt;Overview&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;247&quot; data-end=&quot;855&quot;&gt;The Client and Product Services Team (CAPS) supports KKR’s global distribution and client retention efforts by delivering high-quality, timely, and strategically positioned responses to prospect and existing client information requests. This includes the completion of Requests for Proposals (RFPs), Requests for Information (RFIs), Due Diligence Questionnaires (DDQs), and other client monitoring-related deliverables. The team partners closely with investment, product, legal, compliance, and operations stakeholders to ensure accurate, consistent, and compelling messaging across KKR’s expanding platform.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;857&quot; data-end=&quot;1026&quot;&gt;The Consultant will play a key role in the end-to-end execution of client monitoring requests, contributing to both day-to-day delivery and ongoing process improvements.&lt;/p&gt;
